        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer190503043" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6502349898091913226">If you want to begin to understand how revolution happens, how individuals get to manipulate the mob, how rioters can be triggered to bring down a government or a monarch, this well researched and beautifully written fictionalised account of the French revolution is a good place to start.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


