<li class='cover' id='bookCover_626414'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/626414.Fatal_Purity"><img alt="Fatal Purity: Robespierre and the French Revolution" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1316727446l/626414._SX98_.jpg" />
