<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18263288-choosing-terror"><img alt="Choosing Terror: Virtue, Friendship, and Authenticity in the French Revolution" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/book/111x148-bcc042a9c91a29c1d680899eff700a03.png" />
